Pick up the knife from off of the counter.
Turn around then go straight then right to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Turn around then to the right and go straight to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around then go straight then right to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.

Place the tomato in the microwave, turn it on, open the microwave and remove the tomato.

Place the tomato in the sink.
